OL,3,CEight police officers suspended over
OL,4,Cracism accusation
OL,6,FEight officers have been suspended by
OL,7,FGreater Manchester Police following a
OL,8,Freport of alleged racial
OL,9,Fdiscrimination.
OL,11,FThe force announced on Monday, 29
OL,12,FJuly, it had also placed an officer on
OL,13,Frestricted duties, and referred itself
OL,14,Fto the Independent Office for Police
OL,15,FConduct (IOPC).
