OL,3,CEight police officers suspended over
OL,4,Cracism accusation
OL,6,FThe suspensions are not related the
OL,7,Fincident at Manchester Airport which
OL,8,Fsaw a GMP officer suspended after a
OL,9,Fvideo circulated online of a man
OL,10,Fallegedly being kicked and stamped on
OL,11,Fthe head.
OL,13,FSeven of the suspended officers are
OL,14,Ffrom the Bury district, and one is
OL,15,Ffrom Rochdale who was working in Bury
OL,16,Fat the time of the allegations.
OL,18,FThe force said it has temporarily
OL,19,Frelocated officers to Bury to cover
OL,20,Foperational duties and minimise
OL,21,Fdisruption within the district.
