OL,3,CEight police officers suspended over
OL,4,Cracism accusation
OL,6,FThe head of GMP's professional
OL,7,Fstandards directorate, Detective Chief
OL,8,FSuperintendent Mike Allen, said: "The
OL,9,Freports we have received are deeply
OL,10,Fconcerning and I hope to reassure the
OL,11,Fcommunity of Bury, the wider public,
OL,12,Fand the GMP workforce that a full and
OL,13,Fthorough investigation is being
OL,14,Fconducted into these matters."
OL,16,FThis follows GMP suspending five
OL,17,Fofficers and placing two on restricted
OL,18,Fduties ` all from the Bury district `
OL,19,Fon July 17.
