OL,3,CEight police officers suspended over
OL,4,Cracism accusation
OL,6,FGMP also made a mandatory referral to
OL,7,Fthe IOPC over that case on July 4 and
OL,8,Fthe police watchdog began
OL,9,Finvestigating the following day.
OL,11,FThe IOPC said that referral involved
OL,12,Fallegations the officers "openly
OL,13,Fengaged in conversations and either
OL,14,Fused, or failed to challenge,
OL,15,Foffensive language".
OL,17,FIOPC regional director Catherine Bates
OL,18,Fsaid: "Officers are expected to
OL,19,Fmaintain exemplary standards of
OL,20,Fconduct and professionalism.
